RESEARCH ALERT - Grupo Corvi raised . SBC Warburg analyst Patricia Tyler on Friday raised her rating on Mexico ' s Grupo Corvi SA de CV to buy from hold . - - In a report , Tyler said she raised her rating on the grocery wholesaler because second - quarter earnings were above expectations . - - The quarterly trend " shows a positive momentum for Corvi , " especially for the second half of the year , the report said . - - The year - end price target is 6 . 5 pesos . - - shares closed Thursday at 5 . 16 pesos . ( ( - - Ian Simpson , Wall Street Desk , ( 212 ) 859 - 1879 ) ) 
